soot.toDex.instructions

Class Insn11n

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.toDex.instructions.AbstractInsn
      • soot.toDex.instructions.Insn11n
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, Insn, OneRegInsn

    public class Insn11n
extends AbstractInsn
implements OneRegInsn
    The "11n" instruction format: It needs one 16-bit code unit, has one register and is used for a 4-bit literal (hence the "n" for "nibble").

    It is used by the opcode "const/4".
